Class SessionLoadC

  • java.lang.Object
    • views.session_load.SessionLoadC
  • public class SessionLoadC
extends java.lang.Object
    The controller class for the session load menu. It is called by the view with the user input and it calls the interactor through the SessionLoadIB interface
